title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 4: Rangers, Stars Goalie Trouble, Trouba & More
description:
Episode 4 features Rear Admiral & Ryan Whitney talking Rangers, Stars goalie issues, Jacob Trouba & more. The guys also introduce a new segment, along with #AllRightHamilton.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
